NB. =========================================================
NB.*fss v file string search
NB.-Search file for string, returning indices.
NB.-
NB.-syntax:
NB.+str fss file
fss=: 4 : 0
y=. fboxname y
size=. 1!:4 :: _1: y
if. size -: _1 do. return. end.
blk=. (#x) >. 100000 <. size
r=. i.pos=. 0
while. pos < size do.
  dat=. 1!:11 y,<pos,blk <. size-pos
  r=. r,pos+I. x E. dat
  pos=. pos+blk+1-#x
end.
r
)

