NB.fputs v convert text for file write as string
fputs=: 3 : 0
dat=. ":y
if. 0 e. $dat do.
  ''
else.
  if. 1>:#$dat do.
    toHOST dat,(-.({:dat) e. CRLF) # LF
  else.
    ,dat,"1 toHOST LF
  end.
end.
)

NB. =========================================================
NB.*ftype v get file type
NB.-Get file type, as:
NB.-
NB.- 0 = not exist
NB.- 1 = file
NB.- 2 = directory
ftype=: 3 : 0
NB. windows needs 1!:4 for synchronization
(1:@(1!:4) :: 0:)^:IFWIN < f=. }: ^: ('/' = {:) , > fboxname y
d=. 1!:0 f
if. #d do.
  >: 'd' = 4 { > 4 { ,d
else.
  0
end.
)

